summary: The boots are back! this was difficult due to the nonexistence of Acrobatics in Skyrim
descriptionHtml:
Simply put, the boots give you a perk that reduces falling damage by 3/4. This means it is more effective than the Heavy Armor \"Cushioned\" perk.

I need a veteran papyrus scripter to check my work as i have little ability in papyrus.
Version .75 is on the way as well as location picture although the description below is pretty obvious.

A simple pair of what appear to be bartender shoes rest on the riften thieves guild\'s guild master\'s chest. A pair of boots that they have long since forgotten the significance. Will you take the pair of boots in the ragged flaggon cistern? Will you become Springheeled?
author: jahnarae
